HEADWORD: Swede
<hw>Swede</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. G.
<ets>Schwede</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A native or inhabitant of
Sweden.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A Swedish turnip. See under
<er>Turnip</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Swedenborgian</ent>⟦br⟧
